resources.description: The paper has expatiated the mutual conversion between national and international standards (ISO/IEC 10646), and realized UNICODE operation based on MATLAB. It has made code conversion between national and international standards, in order to provide an effective method for further Tibetan small-character code processing based on MATLAB.
resources.name: The Realization of Tibetan Code Conversion between National and International Standards
